---
import Layout from '../../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Naprej Privacy Policy"
	description="Privacy Policy for Naprej, the Slovenian language-learning app"
	pubDate={new Date('April 26 2026')}
>
	<h2>Privacy Policy for Naprej</h2>
	<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> April 26, 2026</p>

	<h3>Introduction</h3>
	<p>
		Naprej ("we", "our", or "us") is a mobile language-learning app for English speakers learning
		Slovenian. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we
		handle information when you use the Naprej app on iOS or Android.
	</p>

	<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
	<p>
		<strong>Naprej does not collect personally identifiable information.</strong> We do not:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Collect your name, email address, or phone number</li>
		<li>Require you to create an account</li>
		<li>Track your location</li>
		<li>Access your contacts, photos, microphone, or camera</li>
		<li>Use third-party advertising networks or tracking SDKs</li>
		<li>Sell or share data with data brokers</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Analytics</h3>
	<p>
		Naprej collects anonymous usage analytics to help us understand how the app is used and to
		improve the learning experience. This includes information such as which lessons are started
		and completed, which exercise types are most engaging, app crashes and errors, and general
		device information (such as device model and operating system version).
	</p>
	<p>
		This analytics data is not tied to your identity, is not shared with third-party advertisers
		or trackers, and is used solely to improve the app. Naprej does not use third-party tracker
		SDKs from advertising or marketing networks.
	</p>

	<h3>Learning Progress and App Data</h3>
	<p>
		Your lesson progress, vocabulary review history, and any preferences you set within the app
		are stored locally on your device. If you uninstall the app, this data is removed with it.
	</p>

	<h3>Children's Privacy</h3>
	<p>
		Naprej does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone, including children under
		13 years of age. The app is suitable for learners of all ages.
	</p>

	<h3>App Store Information</h3>
	<p>
		When you download Naprej from the Apple App Store or Google Play Store, those platforms may
		collect information according to their own privacy policies. We do not receive personally
		identifiable information from these platforms beyond aggregated, anonymous download and
		crash statistics that the platforms provide to all developers.
	</p>

	<h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
	<p>
		We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this
		page with an updated "Last Updated" date.
	</p>

	<h3>Contact Us</h3>
	<p>
		If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
	</p>
	<p>
		<a href="mailto:evan@mightystrong.io">evan@mightystrong.io</a>
	</p>
</Layout>
